<!--
Guardians create constant auras that provide various bonuses to nearby allies
All genes add their own hediff with the same radius as the original, but only the main "Under the guardian's wing" hediff will be visible
The main one is there to show the player that a pawn is under the effects, and the rest are hidden to avoid flooding the panel
-->